Cabinet dowels/wine Pico project.

Default pins:
- GPIO 15: dowels puzzle solved input
- GPIO 16: wine puzzle solved input
- GPIO 14: reset button to GND, using internal pull-up

MQTT commands:
- escape/post/query
- escape/game/reset

MQTT POST publish:
- escape/post/cubby/2/state = ready or completed
- escape/post/cubby/3/state = ready or completed

When the local reset button is pressed, the Pico republishes these POST states.

Sensor inputs assume external pull-down wiring. Use relay/MOSFET driver boards for any powered devices.
